OL,7,FBritons would face an extra #100 or
OL,8,Fmore on the cost of a fortnight's
OL,9,Fholiday in England if the government
OL,10,Fpushes ahead with plans to allow a
OL,11,Fholiday tax, hospitality and leisure
OL,12,Fbosses have warned.
