OL,3,CHoliday tax would drive jump in cost
OL,4,Cof holidays in England, say industry
OL,5,Cbosses
OL,7,FIn last year's autumn budget, the
OL,8,FChancellor confirmed that English
OL,9,Fregional mayors will have the powers
OL,10,Fto introduce visitor levies on
OL,11,Fovernight stays in hotels, Airbnbs and
OL,12,Fholiday lets.
OL,14,FThe plans, which mirror similar
OL,15,Fdevolved moves in Scotland and Wales,
OL,16,Fare designed to give local mayors more
OL,17,Ffunds to invest in local
OL,18,Finfrastructure and transport.
