OL,3,CHoliday tax would drive jump in cost
OL,4,Cof holidays in England, say industry
OL,5,Cbosses
OL,7,FMayors in London and Liverpool are
OL,8,Falready among those to have welcomed
OL,9,Fthe plans, and indicate they will
OL,10,Fintroduce levies.
OL,12,FIn the letter, the industry bosses
OL,13,Fsaid: "This 'Holiday Tax' will hit
OL,14,Ffamilies hardest, puts jobs at risk,
OL,15,Fdrain money from local businesses and
OL,16,Fcommunities and undermine the
OL,17,FGovernment's growth agenda.
OL,19,F"For millions of hardworking families,
OL,20,Fa UK holiday is their chance to switch
OL,21,Foff and spend quality time together.
